Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.09,0:00:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.73,0:00:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that weird to walk around town\Non Christmas with Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times I try to visualize it,\Nweird things keep happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.99,0:00:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, it's been so cold\Non the second floor of the gym,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.28,0:00:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so we haven't been going up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to spend special time alone with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:51.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Shimamura"\N"Hey, on Christmas..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And to make that happen, I figured\Nthe best bet would be Christmas, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem would be to actually\Nask her to hang out on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:55.18,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Shimamura"\N"Hey, on Christmas..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:00:58.93,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Shimamura"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I just wrote it extra hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.94,0:01:09.44,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Shimamura"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but even after I erased it,\Nyou could still see her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.86,0:01:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of like when I close my eyes\Nto sleep, and even when tomorrow comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't forget about Shimamura
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:18.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Christmas"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"Christmas" from the day before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever Shimamura asks me to do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how much I'd end up complying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:02:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wrong mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Would I try? I probably would.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a nap together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been so wrapped up with trying to ask\NShimamura to hang out on Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I almost went off the edge,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,climbed up a tree,\Nand can't come back down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there, Shimako.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. What? Do I need a reason\Nto talk to my buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo. Studying hard, Adacchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:04:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you are? Wow, how studious of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Alrighty! Let's go to Nagafuji's place today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't shake the feeling that you end up\Nnear our {\i1}kotatsu {\i0}like every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, you're just imagining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait. My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Wait, how is that any different?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you're asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll just keep thinking about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what were you trying to ask me, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:44.65,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Hey, on Christmas..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's study together... or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Study? Then we should invite\NHino and Nagafuji, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they're smarter than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means they'd get nothing\Nout of studying with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. You think that\Nour grades are about the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're about the same level of stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, I'm kidding. Sure.\NWhy don't we study together?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should we study? The library?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe a family restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,At home! At your house!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It's really dusty, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha--?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your room, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about my place...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, that would be\Na bit awkward for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, sure. Let's go to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's dusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:05:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, a friend. Whoa, in our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Whoa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi, was it? Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's go to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for letting me come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't your room this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. My study room is upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:37.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Parakeety" "Croquette" "Li'l Cutlet"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, none of these are doing it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you say how you really feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, how about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is definitely the next mascot\Nfor the Nagafuji Butcher Shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:48.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Nagafuji Butcher Shop"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Li'l Croquette, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess that'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you mean, "That's the one"?\NYou even gave her a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll give you a treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet! Wait, is it another\Nkiss on the forehead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, yeah... I guess I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Auntie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have mandarins, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Close... Are we close?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Not any more than normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we get along like normal friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:08:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I told you it was dusty.\NThis is my study room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Until things warm up, I call for a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you usually listen to music\Nwhile you study, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, pretty often.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,On Ch... Chri...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what kind of kid were you, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Pretty normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I was always the kid\Nserving lunch to the other kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I think my hair was shorter,\Nand not dyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura with short hair... With black hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you like, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! I, uh... haven't really changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... I picture you holding\Nthe preschool teacher's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what were you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was, uh... I'm particular\Nabout whose hand I hold...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck am I saying?!\NNow I sound like I'm asking her out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... I wonder why you hold mine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, uh, earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura had asked why it was her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? It's rather simple, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to just come out and say that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd basically be saying,\N"I love you, Shimamura."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If she woke up and you were kissing her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd really be game over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not like I\Nabsolutely need to kiss her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I wouldn't be opposed\Nif Shimamura asked for one...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But she didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, I was just--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is much softer and pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A-Ah, I shee...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you a little sleepyhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure am...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Shimamura... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Chri...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you usually do on Christmas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We get fried chicken for dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My little sister still believes\Nin Santa Claus, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Santa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How long did you believe in Santa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? I didn't, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way a nice old man\Nlike that actually exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:12:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought... he was at my preschool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's because the only people to ever\Ntalk about Santa were at my preschool...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we both sorta sucked at childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know... I think we were dumber\Nand more uninhibited when we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing we survived at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be nice. Probably never experienced\Nstiff shoulders back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I just want to stay\Nlike this with Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I'm protecting my precious\Nchild with my wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi's been acting weird lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel her staring at me a lot more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first weird thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The second thing is when we're talking,\Nshe seems to always be holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure how her lips haven't cramped yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And the third thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm going to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She scored higher on\Nour English test than I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Though the third thing has\Nnothing to do with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:39.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Shimamura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry! Actually, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just having a little bit of fun.\NMore importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.62,0:13:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, take a deep breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:13:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Adacchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer if you didn't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear not. I probably won't use\Nthat nickname again. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just been wondering what's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always staring at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you want to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorta...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this winter... I mean, next week, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In about ten days...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten days?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I, uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got this, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you after I think on it some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:15:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a girl I was really close\Nwith in kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She would always hide behind me and\Nto put it simply, she was like Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is when I was still unguarded,\Nstill had interest in everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and dove headfirst into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She really loved sparkly things\Nlike marbles and wind chimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only when she found sparkly things
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that she'd leave my side and run towards them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look at the image\Ntrending on social media today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You got your lunch bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:44.42,On Top,,0,0,0,,Oh? They both have their hands raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You should get to school, too, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shush your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,High schoolers only need to get to\Nschool before the sun goes up fully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who taught you that dumb rule? Hurry and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis! Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend is here! That girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh... Friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that came over the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How ya doin', Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Heyo... Mornin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying to sound like a jock?\NSo, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit early, isn't it?\NActually, when did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:17:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to stop by somewhere...\NThis is pretty normal, and I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold, so let's talk inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Help her eat, would you? She's so slow,\NI just don't know what to do with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to say any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I ate at home, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.47,0:17:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... One bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to eat more!\NDoesn't your mom tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As a mom, you feel better when your\Ndaughter is a bit pudgy and doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,wither away worrying about her waistline.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't. We don't really talk much.\NShe's rarely home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fanks for the grub.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go talk in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeesh, it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I just turned the heater on,\Nso make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you that yesterday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go out somewhere... or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Sure... Wait, that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, but after school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean like right now\Nand skip school, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not today... you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering about the 25th of this month!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The 25th? The 25th...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,December 25th... Oh, that 25th.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Christmas, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh--?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost asked her why, but I stopped myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why Christmas? Why with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If I asked her why, I felt like\Nthe backbone of our relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,would get bent out of shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It would take a bunch of time\Nand effort to fix it later,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and I wondered if I'd even bother with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,though the answer was sadly pretty clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't really thought it out at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:19:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what did you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't really thought it out at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to think that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi never got to have\Nthe full Christmas experience
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's why she asked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, just looking at how she's\Nacting and how red her face is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's basically like...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She's asking me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's not a big deal or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I just... I think I just\Nmaybe wanted to hang out
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,with someone on a fun day like Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not maybe. I do want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She just wanted to hang out with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And she doesn't have any other friends,\Nso that's why she asked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't have to be me specifically. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:21:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to be home by dinner,\Nbut if you're okay with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to decide where\Nwe're going to go and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.23,0:21:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wittle puppy Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We should get to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Right... Then let's go together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us hurry. Yes. Oh, I'm going to be so busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.18,0:21:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for li'l ol' me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:21:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I go all old timey?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me catch a ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.24,0:22:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I guess I'm hanging out\Nwith Adachi this Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's not like Santa's coming by,\Neven if I waited at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.96,0:22:22.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 5: 'Adachi's Question'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.05,0:24:07.05,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Next Time: 'White Album'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.07,0:23:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Adashimapedia: {\i1}Kotatsu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.24,0:23:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kotatsu {\i0}tables just ruin everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.62,0:23:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.71,0:24:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. I'm not leaving this warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do the preview.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.29,0:24:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, too cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.25,0:24:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.21,0:24:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good.
